title: {LAVteam} GEDCO OMNI 3D Design x86 x64 v11.000
description:
Program name:	GEDCO OMNI 3D Design v11.000
     Protection type:	HASP, RLM, SPro
     Build date:	24/10/2011

     Instructions:	Unrar and install the application.
			Copy \patch\RLM\ folder to the <installdir>
			Set up new system variable (my computer ->
			properties -> advance -> environment variables ->
			system variable):
			RLM_LIC_HOST = 28000@<your_host_name>
			Restart PC.
			Edit Gedco_Key_Number_0.lic (in the above
			mentioned already copied RLM folder):
			replace (computer Name) in the first string
			with your computer name (<your_host_name>)
			Excute rlm and keep it running.
			Run then app.
